text: The Kent Coast line is a railway line in Kent linking to . == Services == Train services are run by Southeastern. ==Trains== The main trains used on the line are Class 375 Electrostars. ==Gallery== File:Network SouthEast train at Dover Priory station, Kent.jpg|Network SouthEast Class 411 at Dover Priory railway station in 1994 File:Ramsgate railway station in 2008.jpg|Class 375 at Ramsgate railway station ==Other websites== * Category:Railway lines of Kent
